SELECT celebrity_id, designer_id, collaboration_details FROM fashion_collaborations WHERE collaboration_details LIKE '%Fashion Week%'

SELECT designer_city, COUNT(designer_name) AS total_collaborations FROM designer_portfolio GROUP BY designer_city ORDER BY total_collaborations DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT celebrity_name FROM celebrity_collaborations;
SELECT * FROM celebrity_collaborations c JOIN designer_portfolio d ON c.designer_name = d.designer_name WHERE d.designer_age > 30 AND c.collaboration_date < '2023-01-01';
SELECT * FROM celebrity;
SELECT celebrity_name, profession FROM celebrity WHERE profession='Actor';

SELECT celebrity_name, designer_name FROM celebrity INNER JOIN collaboration ON celebrity.celebrity_id = collaboration.celebrity_id INNER JOIN designer ON designer.designer_id = collaboration.designer_id;
SELECT * FROM designer WHERE brand_name='Gucci';

SELECT celebrity_name, designer_name, collaboration_date FROM celebrity INNER JOIN collaboration ON celebrity.celebrity_id = collaboration.celebrity_id INNER JOIN designer ON designer.designer_id = collaboration.designer_id ORDER BY collaboration_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM celebrity;
SELECT celebrity_name, profession FROM celebrity ORDER BY celebrity_name DESC;
SELECT c.collaboration_date, ce.celebrity_name, d.designer_name FROM collaboration c JOIN celebrity ce ON c.celebrity_id = ce.celebrity_id JOIN designer d ON c.designer_id = d.designer_id;

SELECT ce.celebrity_name, d.designer_name FROM collaboration c JOIN celebrity ce ON c.celebrity_id = ce.celebrity_id JOIN designer d ON c.designer_id = d.designer_id WHERE c.collaboration_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT DISTINCT ce.celebrity_name FROM collaboration c JOIN celebrity ce ON c.celebrity_id = ce.celebrity_id WHERE d.designer_name LIKE '%Gucci%';
SELECT * FROM celebrity;
SELECT celebrity_name, age, nationality FROM celebrity WHERE profession='Singer';
SELECT celebrity_name, designer_name, collaboration_type FROM fashion_collaborations ORDER BY collaboration_date DESC;
SELECT celebrity_name, designer_name, brand_name FROM fashion_collaborations JOIN designer ON fashion_collaborations.designer_name = designer.designer_name;
SELECT celebrity_name, profession, age, nationality FROM celebrity WHERE nationality='USA' ORDER BY age;
SELECT * FROM fashion_collaborations ORDER BY collaboration_date DESC;
SELECT celebrity_name, designer_name FROM fashion_collaborations WHERE collaboration_type='Fashion Show';
SELECT celebrity_name, profession, age FROM celebrity WHERE nationality='American' AND age > 30;
SELECT designer_name, brand_name, country FROM designer WHERE founded_year < 2000 ORDER BY designer_name ASC;

SELECT fc.collaboration_date, c.celebrity_name, d.designer_name FROM fashion_collaborations fc JOIN celebrity c ON fc.celebrity_name = c.celebrity_name JOIN designer d ON fc.designer_name = d.designer_name WHERE fc.collaboration_type='Collaboration' ORDER BY fc.collaboration_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM celebrities;
SELECT name, age FROM designers ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT celebrity_id, name, nationality FROM celebrities WHERE nationality = 'American';
SELECT name, design_style FROM designers WHERE age > 30;
SELECT c.collaboration_id, ci.item_name, ci.item_type FROM collaborations c JOIN clothing_items ci ON c.collaboration_id = ci.item_id;
SELECT * FROM celebrities WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT celebrity_id, name, nationality FROM celebrities WHERE nationality = 'American';

SELECT c.collaboration_id, c.collaboration_date, ce.name AS celebrity_name, d.name AS designer_name, ci.item_name FROM collaborations c JOIN celebrities ce ON c.celebrity_id = ce.celebrity_id JOIN designers d ON c.designer_id = d.designer_id JOIN collaborations_clothing cc ON c.collaboration_id = cc.collaboration_id JOIN clothing_items ci ON cc.item_id = ci.item_id WHERE cc.quantity > 10 ORDER BY c.collaboration_date DESC;

SELECT ce.name, COUNT(cc.quantity) AS total_items FROM celebrities ce JOIN collaborations c ON ce.celebrity_id = c.celebrity_id JOIN collaborations_clothing cc ON c.collaboration_id = cc.collaboration_id GROUP BY ce.name HAVING total_items > 5;

SELECT d.name AS designer_name, COUNT(c.collaboration_id) AS total_collaborations, SUM(cc.quantity) AS total_items FROM designers d JOIN collaborations c ON d.designer_id = c.designer_id JOIN collaborations_clothing cc ON c.collaboration_id = cc.collaboration_id GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY total_collaborations DESC, total_items DESC;
